le\u2019s daily life by delivering in-home respiratory care and durable medical equipment to 135 centers in 26 states. They\u2019re all about respirators, and with</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1291085789/image_1291085789.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745492-struggling-for-air-quipt-home-medical-stock-growth-hurdles-recovery-potential-hold-for-now", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 09:47:02", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745498", "title": "CB Leading Economic Index: Small Rise In November", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Man in a business meeting using an interactive screen while giving a presentation\" data-id=\"1468025006\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Hispanolistic</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The latest <a href=\"https://www.conference-board.org/topics/us-leading-indicators\" rel=\"noopener noopener\">Conference Board Leading Economic Index</a> (LEI) increased slightly in November. The index rose 0.3% from the previous month to 99.7 after eight consecutive monthly declines.</p> <blockquote><p>\"The US LEI rose in November for the first time since February</p></blockquote>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745498-cb-leading-economic-index-small-rise-november", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 09:30:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745491", "title": "Okeanis Eco Tankers: Targeting Efficiency Gains With One Of The Youngest Fleets In The Industry", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1324124760/image_1324124760.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Aerial view on the industrial cargo ship unloading at the petroleum terminal in New Jersey, on the Arthur Kill tidal strait at the border with New York State.\" data-id=\"1324124760\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"863px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1324124760/image_1324124760.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1324124760/image_1324124760.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1324124760/image_1324124760.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1324124760/image_1324124760.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_image