"<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1208318678/image_1208318678.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Manager is showing Treasury Inflation Protected Securities TIPs.\" data-id=\"1208318678\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5000px\" height=\"3750px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1208318678/image_1208318678.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1208318678/image_1208318678.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1208318678/image_1208318678.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1208318678/image_1208318678.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1208318678/image_1208318678.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1208318678/image_1208318678.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1208318678/image_1208318678.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1208318678/image_1208318678.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">designer491</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Over the past two years, I've authored several articles detailing the case for TIPS in a diversified all-weather portfolio:</p> <ul> <li>A reliable source of regular income above the inflation rate for retirees that can serve as a low-cost, do-it-yourself annuity.</li> </ul>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1208318678/image_1208318678.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745488-tips-for-reliable-income-year-end-update", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 08:02:05", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4740958", "title": "Politics And The Markets 12/20/24", "description": "<p><span>This is the forum for daily political discussion on Seeking Alpha. A new version is published every market day.</span></p> <p>Please don't leave political comments on other articles or posts on the site.</p> <p>The comments below are not regulated with the same rigor as the rest of the site, and this is an <strong>'enter at your own risk' </strong>area as discussion can get very heated. If you can't stand the heat... you know what they say...</p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span>More on Today's Markets:</span></b></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span></span></b></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Moderation Guidelines:</b></p> <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b><span></span></b>We remove comments under the following categories:</p> <ul> <li>Personal attacks on another user account</li> <li>Anti-Vaxxer or covid related misinformation</li> <li>Stereotyping, prejudiced or racist language about individuals or the topic under discussion.</li> <li>Inciting violence messages, encouraging hate groups and political violence.</li> </ul> <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Regardless of which side of the political divide you find yourself, please be courteous and don't direct abuse at other users.</p> <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">For any issue with regards to comments please email us at : moderation@seekingalpha.com.</p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span>Seeking Alpha's Disclosure:</span></b><span> Past performance is no guarantee of future results. No recommendation or advice is being given as to whether any investment is suitable for a particular investor. Any views or opinions expressed above may not reflect those of Seeking Alpha as a whole. Seeking Alpha is not a licensed securities dealer, broker or US investment adviser or investment bank. Our analysts are third party authors that include both professional investors and individual investors who may not be licensed or certified by any institute or regulatory body.</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"> </p> <div class=\"before_last_paragraph-piano-placeholder\"></div> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span></span></b></p> <div class=\"sa-art article-width paywall-full-content\" id=\"a-body\"><span class=\"content-end p p1\"></span></div>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4740958-politics-and-the-markets-122024", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 08:00:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745487", "title": "Rigetti Computing: Be Wary Of The Overhyped Catalyst", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1493756157/image_1493756157.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Attention sign 3d rendered isolated on white background with shadow\" data-id=\"1493756157\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1034px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1493756157/image_1493756157.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1493756157/image_1493756157.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1493756157/image_1493756157.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1493756157/image_1493756157.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1493756157/image_1493756157.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1493756157/image_1493756157.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1493756157/image_1493756157.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1493756157/image_1493756157.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Anthony Paz - Photographer/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Thesis</h2> <p>I am perplexed by the sharp rise in Rigetti Computing (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RGTI\" title=\"Rigetti Computing, Inc.\">RGTI</a></span>) (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RGTIW\" title=\"Rigetti Computing, Inc. WT EXP\">RGTIW</a></span>):</p> <ol> <li>RGTI is unlikely to benefit materially from NQI funding</li> <li>Management has a patchy record in revenue and margins execution</li> </ol>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1493756157/image_1493756157.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745487-rigetti-computing-stock-be-wary-of-overhyped-catalyst-hold", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 07:42:56", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745483", "title": "Dogecoin: The Gains Have Been Made (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359687309/image_1359687309.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Dogecoin cryptocurrency coin\" data-id=\"1359687309\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1023px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359687309/image_1359687309.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359687309/image_1359687309.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359687309/image_1359687309.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.co